                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="pdpt-bg-left mt-0">
                    <div class="pdpt-title">
                        <h4> 2: TIKBASKET FAIMLY MEMBER CARD RS: 4999</h4>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="top-posts">
                        <li>
                            <div class="blog-top-item">
                                <span class="blog-time"> BENEFIT:  </span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="blog-top-item">

                                <span class="blog-time"> • MONEY WILL BE ADJUST IN FIRST BILLING </span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="blog-top-item">
                                <span class="blog-time"> • FIRST BILLING FLAT 10% OFF </span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="blog-top-item">
                                <span class="blog-time"> • ONE YEARS ALL DELIVERY UPTO RS 500 IS FREE</span>
